title: SCOTUS Battle to Replace RBG, Rep. Matt Gaetz
itunes:title: SCOTUS Battle to Replace RBG, Rep. Matt Gaetz
description:
Guests: Congressman Matt Gaetz, a Republican from Florida's first congressional district, Kriti Gupta, Bloomberg Markets Live reporter, Morgan Ortagus, State Department Spokesperson, Jeanne Zaino, Iona College professor and Bloomberg politics contributor, Lester Munson, Principal at government relations firm, BGR Group, and Congressman Denver Riggleman, a Republican representing Virginia's 5th congressional district.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
